en punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'https://google.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o redirect no javascript es6","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-redirect/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-reduceSuccessive/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o reduceSuccessive no javascript es6"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-recordAnimationFrames/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o recordAnimationFrames no javascript es6"}}}}}